#proof[
  $f : RR -> RR$ continuous $<=>$ for all $G subset.eq RR$ open, $f^(-1) (G)$ open. For all $a < b in RR$, then $f^(-1) ((a, b))$ open so $f^(-1) ((a, b)) in cal(M)$ so $f$ measurable.

