  dots.v & wide dots.v  & wide  dots.up & wide  dots.v & wide dots.v\
  phi_(1, k) & wide phi_(2, k) & wide dots.up & wide phi_(k,k) & wide phi_(k+1, k) & wide dots.c \
  dots.v & wide dots.v  & wide  dots.up & wide  dots.v & wide dots.v & wide dots.c \
