  integral_RR |f_n - f|^p <= integral_(RR \\ [-n,n]) |f|^p + integral_({|f| > n}) |f|^p -> 0 "as" n-> infinity.  
  $
]

#lemma[
Simple functions are dense in $L^p (RR)$.
